<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Welcome to Task Pro</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #1f2937;"
  >
    <table
      role='presentation'
      cellspacing='0'
      cellpadding='0'
      style='max-width: 640px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden; width: 100%;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td
          style='padding: 30px; background-color: #BEDBB0; text-align: center;'
        >
          <h1
            style='margin: 0; font-size: 28px; color: #161616; font-weight: 600;'
          >Welcome to Task Pro</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style='padding: 24px;'>
          <p
            style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 16px 0;'
          >Hi {{userName}},</p>
          <p
            style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 16px 0;'
          >
            We’re thrilled to welcome you to Task Pro, your new go-to
            application for efficient task and project management!
          </p>
          <p
            style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 16px 0;'
          >With Task Pro, you can:</p>
          <ul
            style='margin: 0 0 16px 16px; padding: 0; color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'
          >
            <li>Create boards and cards to organize tasks and projects
              effectively.</li>
            <li>Drag and drop cards to track progress and priorities seamlessly.</li>
            <li>Collaborate with your team effortlessly and stay on top of every
              detail.</li>
          </ul>
          <p
            style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 16px 0;'
          >
            Your account is now set up, and you’re ready to explore all the
            features Task Pro offers to make your workflow smoother and more
            productive.
          </p>
          <p
            style='font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; margin: 16px 0;'
          >
            If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reply to
            this email or visit our
            <a
              href='{{supportLink}}'
              style='color: #BEDBB0; text-decoration: none;'
              onmouseover="this.style.color='#9DC888';"
              onmouseout="this.style.color='#BEDBB0';"
            >
              Support Center
            </a>.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td
          style='text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9fafb; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;'
        >
          <p style='margin: 0;'>&copy;
            {{year}}
            Task Pro. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p style='margin: 0;'>
            <a
              href='{{privacyPolicyLink}}'
              target='_blank'
              style='color: #BEDBB0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px;'
            >Privacy Policy</a>
            |
            <a
              href='{{supportLink}}'
              target='_blank'
              style='color: #BEDBB0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px;'
            >Contact Support</a>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>